---
title: Beef Steak with Pan Gravy with Roasted Garlic Smashed Potatoes and Shallot Green Beans
description: Grab a blanket and cozy up for this stick-to-your-ribs feast. Roasted garlic adds a lovely warm and rustic touch to the savoury steak and green beans.
